          "level": 2,
          "text": "Return Value",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The return value, if any, of the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "body",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " closure.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If you call this function from the body of an asynchronous function,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the unsafe task handle passed to the closure is always non-",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "nil",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "because an asynchronous function always runs in the context of a task.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "However, if you call this function from the body of a synchronous function,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "and that function isn’t executing in the context of any task,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the unsafe task handle is ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "nil",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Don’t store an unsafe task reference",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "for use outside this method’s closure.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Storing an unsafe reference doesn’t affect the task’s actual life cycle,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "and the behavior of accessing an unsafe task reference",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "outside of the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "withUnsafeCurrentTask(body:)",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " method’s closure isn’t defined.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "There’s no safe way to retrieve a reference to the current task",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "and save it for long-term use.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "To query the current task without saving a reference to it,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "use properties like ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "currentPriority",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "If you need to store a reference to a task,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "create an unstructured task using ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "Task.detached(priority:operation:)",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " instead.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
